Step 1 — Prerequisites (one-time)
----------------------------------

  brew install azure-cli
  az login
  az account set --subscription 8ecb7c89-073f-45a8-88b5-49ef2708228b


Step 2 — Create resource group + ACR (one-time)
------------------------------------------------

