Step 4 — Deploy infrastructure (Bicep)
----------------------------------------
Run once to create everything: VNet, PostgreSQL, Redis, Key Vault, Storage,
App Services, Front Door + WAF, all role assignments. Takes ~10-15 minutes.

  cd infrastructure/bicep

  az deployment group create \
    --resource-group servisite-rg \
    --template-file main.bicep \
    --parameters @parameters.json \
    --parameters @parameters.secrets.json

On re-deploy (e.g. after adding new env vars), run the same command again —
Bicep is idempotent, it only updates what changed.


